WEBVTT

00:00.334 --> 00:03.769
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON</i>
<i> "SECRETS AND LIES"...</i>
Kevin:
YOU GOT SCOTT MURPHY TURNED IN

00:03.771 --> 00:05.070
AND FORCED THE RICHARDSONS
TO LEAVE.

00:05.072 --> 00:06.171
NOW YOU'RE
PESTERING LISA?

00:06.173 --> 00:07.406
YOU JUST WON'T
BE HAPPY

00:07.408 --> 00:08.774
UNTIL THE WHOLE NEIGHBORHOOD
IS GONE.

00:08.776 --> 00:10.142
YOU'RE A REPORTER?

00:10.144 --> 00:11.377
THERE IS NO STORY.
I'M NOT GUILTY.

00:11.379 --> 00:13.112
THERE'S ALWAYS A STORY.

00:15.616 --> 00:18.217
YOU TEXTED ME.
YOU ASKED ME TO COME.
NO, I DIDN'T.

00:18.219 --> 00:21.186
WHOEVER DID THIS KNOWS HOW
TO GET CLASSIFIED INFORMATION.

00:21.188 --> 00:23.322
THIS IS SERIOUS.
YOU NEED TO WATCH YOUR BACK.

00:24.759 --> 00:25.791
[ BANGING ON DOOR ]

00:25.793 --> 00:27.126
[ LIGHT SWITCH CLICKS ]

00:27.128 --> 00:30.129
Ben: HEY! HEY!

00:35.403 --> 00:37.403
[ PANTING ]

00:37.405 --> 00:39.405
[ GLASS CLINKING ]

00:39.407 --> 00:42.708
Cornell:
DID YOU HURT YOURSELF WHEN YOU
BROKE THE WINDOW, MR. CRAWFORD?

00:42.710 --> 00:44.693
[ MOTOR WHIRS ]

00:44.694 --> 00:46.677
IF YOU NEED MEDICAL ATTENTION,
I CAN HAVE E.M.S. COME BACK.

00:46.680 --> 00:48.480
I'M FINE.

00:48.482 --> 00:49.782
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

00:49.784 --> 00:51.450
HOW COULD THEY DO THIS?

00:51.452 --> 00:53.485
THEY HACKED INTO YOUR TRUCK'S
SECURITY SYSTEM,

00:53.487 --> 00:56.055
KILLED THE POWER, FRYING
THE IGNITION SWITCH REMOTELY.

00:56.057 --> 00:57.523
WHO THE HELL
CAN DO THAT?

00:57.525 --> 01:00.626
VERY FEW PEOPLE ARE CAPABLE OF
COVERING THEIR TRACKS THIS WELL.

01:00.628 --> 01:03.062
WE ALSO
WEREN'T ABLE TO TRACE

01:03.064 --> 01:05.064
THE REAL SOURCE OF THE TEXT
I RECEIVED FROM YOUR NUMBER.

01:05.066 --> 01:07.066
WHY WOULD SOMEONE
DO THIS?

01:07.068 --> 01:10.069
PUBLIC PERCEPTION IS THAT
YOU MURDERED A CHILD.

01:10.071 --> 01:13.739
YEAH, BECAUSE THAT'S WHAT
YOU WANTED THEM TO THINK.

01:13.741 --> 01:17.209
DEAD CHILDREN TEND TO ELICIT
A HEIGHTENED EMOTIONAL RESPONSE.

01:17.211 --> 01:20.846
WHOEVER DID THIS,
THEY WATCHED, THEY WAITED.

01:20.848 --> 01:23.849
YOU HAVE A STALKER,
MR. CRAWFORD.

01:23.851 --> 01:25.517
YOU MEAN ASIDE FROM YOU?

01:25.519 --> 01:26.752
YOU'LL NEED
POLICE PROTECTION.

01:26.754 --> 01:28.787
I CAN ASSIGN A DETAIL TO YOU
IMMEDIATELY.

01:28.789 --> 01:30.122
NO.

01:30.124 --> 01:31.457
E-EXCUSE ME?

01:31.459 --> 01:34.426
YOU WANT PERMISSION
TO FOLLOW ME AROUND

01:34.428 --> 01:36.728
SO YOU CAN SEND ME TO PRISON
FOR SOMETHING I DIDN'T DO.

01:36.730 --> 01:39.098
THIS IS FOR
YOUR OWN SAFETY.

01:39.100 --> 01:40.833
I'LL TAKE MY CHANCES.

01:45.739 --> 01:48.240
Christy: HEY.

01:48.242 --> 01:49.575
EXCUSE ME.

01:50.578 --> 01:51.643
YOU ALL RIGHT?

01:51.645 --> 01:52.644
I'M FINE.

01:52.646 --> 01:54.213
I-I GOT LOCKED
IN THE TRUCK.

01:54.215 --> 01:56.348
BEN,
SOMEONE'S AFTER YOU.

01:56.350 --> 01:57.783
CORNELL'S
LOOKING INTO IT.

01:57.785 --> 01:59.885
YEAH, LIKE SHE'S LOOKING
INTO TOM'S MURDER.

01:59.887 --> 02:01.120
GO AHEAD.

02:01.122 --> 02:02.455
HAVE A GOOD NIGHT.

02:02.456 --> 02:03.789
Woman: SHE'LL LEAVE
WHEN HE GETS LOCKED UP.

02:03.791 --> 02:04.790
I JUST FEEL
FOR THOSE POOR KIDS.

02:04.792 --> 02:06.258
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

02:06.260 --> 02:07.259
DON'T.
IT'S NOT WORTH IT.

02:07.261 --> 02:08.627
THIS IS JU--

02:08.629 --> 02:09.828
MY LIFE NOW.

02:09.830 --> 02:12.598
[ SIGHS ]
YOUR LIFE SUCKS.

02:12.600 --> 02:13.832
LET'S GO HOME.

02:20.341 --> 02:22.141
DAVE:
Are you guys okay?

02:22.143 --> 02:23.542
[ LIGHT SWITCH CLICKS ]
WE'RE FINE.

02:23.544 --> 02:25.377
[ Sighing ] Oh, man.

02:25.379 --> 02:27.012
IT'S LIKE
THE GUY'S LEX LUTHOR.

02:27.013 --> 02:28.646
IT'S LIKE YOU'RE DEALING WITH
AN EVIL GENIUS OVER HERE, MAN.

02:28.649 --> 02:29.815
SO WE KNOW
IT'S NOT YOU, THEN.

02:29.817 --> 02:31.750
[ SIGHS ]
SERIOUSLY, MAN, I'M SCARED.

02:31.752 --> 02:33.252
MAYBE YOU SHOULD COME OVER HERE
AND STAY WITH ME.

02:33.254 --> 02:35.004
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

02:35.005 --> 02:36.755
WHAT EXACTLY ARE YOU GONNA DO
TO PROTECT ME?

02:36.757 --> 02:38.490
I GOT A BAT.

02:38.492 --> 02:40.325
Couple of nunchakus.

02:41.495 --> 02:44.496
ALL RIGHT.
I'M HANGING UP.

02:44.498 --> 02:46.498
[ BEEP ]

02:46.500 --> 02:47.799
DAVE IS CONCERNED.

02:47.801 --> 02:49.434
I AGREE WITH HIM.

02:49.436 --> 02:50.669
THAT'S SCARY.

02:51.839 --> 02:53.539
WHO DO YOU THINK'S
DOING THIS?

02:54.875 --> 02:57.476
UH, THEY SENT AN UNTRACEABLE
TEXT TO MY PHONE.

02:57.478 --> 02:59.344
THERE'S NOT A LOT OF PEOPLE
WHO CAN DO THAT

02:59.346 --> 03:01.613
EXCEPT FOR
GOVERNMENT TYPES.

03:01.615 --> 03:03.882
[ SIGHS ]

03:03.884 --> 03:05.918
IF I SAY IT OUT LOUD,
YOU'RE GONNA TELL ME I'M CRAZY.

03:05.920 --> 03:07.403
[ SCOFFS LIGHTLY ]

03:07.404 --> 03:08.887
YOU PASSED CRAZY
ABOUT 10 MILES BACK.

03:08.889 --> 03:10.923
GO FOR IT.

03:10.925 --> 03:13.759
ALL RIGHT, WELL,
WE KNOW KEVIN SERVED.

03:14.862 --> 03:17.563
RIGHT? AND THEN HE WORKED
FOR THE STATE DEPARTMENT.

03:18.632 --> 03:20.566
BUT JUST THINK
ABOUT THIS.

03:20.567 --> 03:22.501
WHEN WE MOVED IN,
KEVIN AND ELAINE BROUGHT US PIE.

03:22.503 --> 03:24.269
HE LENT ME HIS DRILL
AND HIS MOWER,

03:24.271 --> 03:26.638
THEN ALL OF A SUDDEN,
ONE DAY, IT STOPS.

03:26.640 --> 03:28.840
WHY?

03:28.842 --> 03:30.442
[ BOOK THUDS ]

03:30.444 --> 03:31.944
I KNOW I'M RIGHT.
I JUST HAVE TO PROVE IT.

03:31.946 --> 03:33.612
OH, WHY NOT?

03:33.613 --> 03:35.279
YOU WENT AFTER SCOTT,
THE RICHARDSONS, MATT DALY.

03:35.282 --> 03:36.281
WHAT'S ONE MORE?

03:36.283 --> 03:37.482
SO, WHAT SHOULD I DO,

03:37.484 --> 03:39.551
WAIT FOR KEVIN TO MAKE
HIS NEXT MOVE?

03:40.955 --> 03:43.855
[ SIGHS ]
YOU DON'T KNOW IT'S KEVIN.

03:43.857 --> 03:46.892
JUST BEFORE YOU RUIN
ANY MORE DINNER PARTIES,

03:46.894 --> 03:48.594
PLEASE GO OVER THERE
AND TALK TO HIM.

03:48.596 --> 03:50.963
I'M NOT DENYING
THAT HE HATES YOU.

03:50.965 --> 03:52.231
JUST ASK HIM WHY.

03:53.267 --> 03:54.533
OKAY.

03:54.535 --> 03:55.534
REALLY?

03:58.405 --> 03:59.605
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

04:01.408 --> 04:02.674
[ DOOR OPENS ]

04:06.380 --> 04:08.447
[ CELLPHONE RINGING, VIBRATING ]

04:11.252 --> 04:12.317
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

04:14.421 --> 04:17.456
[ CHATTER ]

04:17.458 --> 04:18.523
SEE YOU
AT THE PERP WALK, BEN.

04:18.525 --> 04:20.726
YEAH, THANKS
FOR THE HOSPITALITY.

04:22.630 --> 04:24.396
WHAT'S GOING ON?

04:24.398 --> 04:26.899
NEW STORY.

04:26.900 --> 04:29.401
TEENAGE GIRL KIDNAPPED
BY HER FATHER IN WILMINGTON.

04:29.403 --> 04:31.536
JUST LIKE THAT,
THEY'RE GONE.

04:31.538 --> 04:32.871
JUST LIKE THAT.

04:32.873 --> 04:35.574
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

04:35.576 --> 04:37.442
DID YOU NEED SOMETHING,
BEN?

04:37.444 --> 04:38.844
KEVIN AROUND?

04:38.846 --> 04:40.412
UH, NO.

04:40.414 --> 04:41.580
YOU KNOW
WHEN HE'LL BE BACK?

04:41.582 --> 04:43.048
NO.

04:44.785 --> 04:45.884
SOMETHING WRONG, ELAINE?

04:47.554 --> 04:49.888
I ALWAYS TRY TO SEE
THE BEST IN EVERYONE,

04:49.890 --> 04:52.624
AND YOU ALWAYS APPEAR
TO BE A GOOD MAN, BUT --

04:52.626 --> 04:55.627
BUT THIS --
THIS HAS TO STOP, BEN.

04:55.629 --> 04:57.562
<i> YOU</i> NEED TO STOP.

04:57.564 --> 04:59.064
STOP WHAT EXACTLY?

04:59.066 --> 05:01.300
MY SON WAS KILLED.

05:01.302 --> 05:02.668
OH, SO NOW HE'S<i> YOUR</i> SON.

05:02.670 --> 05:04.803
SEEMS TO ME THAT SCOTT
WAS TOM'S FATHER.

05:04.805 --> 05:06.972
OF COURSE HE WAS.

05:06.974 --> 05:08.507
I KNOW THAT.
DO YOU?

05:08.509 --> 05:09.975
BECAUSE LATELY,
YOU'VE BEEN ACTING

05:09.977 --> 05:11.543
LIKE THE FATHER
OF A MURDERED CHILD.

05:11.545 --> 05:13.545
YOU DIDN'T RAISE HIM,

05:13.546 --> 05:15.546
AND YOU SURE AS HELL
DIDN'T LOVE HIM LIKE SCOTT DID.

05:15.549 --> 05:16.648
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK?

05:16.650 --> 05:18.850
IS THAT WHAT KEVIN'S
PROBLEM WITH ME IS?

05:18.852 --> 05:20.852
KEVIN HAS HIS OWN ISSUES
WITH YOU.

05:20.854 --> 05:22.954
I'M JUST TELLING YOU
LIKE I SEE IT.

05:24.091 --> 05:26.958
WE'VE KNOWN EACH OTHER
FOR YEARS.

05:26.960 --> 05:28.860
YOU CAN'T POSSIBLY THINK THAT
I HAD ANYTHING TO DO WITH --

05:28.862 --> 05:30.829
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO THINK, BEN,
EITHER WAY.

05:30.831 --> 05:32.614
I'M FIGHTING FOR MY LIFE,
ELAINE.

05:32.615 --> 05:34.398
AND YOU'RE DESTROYING
EVERYONE ELSE'S IN THE PROCESS,

05:34.401 --> 05:36.034
STIRRING UP THINGS
THAT NEED TO BE LEFT ALONE.

05:36.036 --> 05:37.803
WHEN IS IT ENOUGH, BEN?

05:37.805 --> 05:39.705
I'M NOT DESTROYING PEOPLE.
THEIR SECRETS ARE.

05:39.707 --> 05:41.039
THAT'S NOT MY PROBLEM.

05:41.041 --> 05:44.910
YOUR PROBLEM IS YOU ONLY
THINK ABOUT YOURSELF.

05:45.646 --> 05:47.012
I KNOW IT'S YOU.

05:48.949 --> 05:52.050
AND I KNOW IT WAS YOU.

05:52.052 --> 05:54.586
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

05:54.588 --> 05:55.887
Cornell:
MR. CRAWFORD.

06:05.899 --> 06:08.066
I TOLD YOU
I DON'T WANT A DETAIL.

06:08.068 --> 06:10.569
I'LL RESPECT THAT.

06:10.571 --> 06:13.004
HOWEVER, YOU SHOULD KNOW
THIS WILL ESCALATE.

06:13.006 --> 06:15.741
AND WHILE YOUR FAMILY
DOESN'T SEEM TO BE THE TARGET,

06:15.743 --> 06:17.576
THEY COULD BECOME
COLLATERAL DAMAGE

06:17.578 --> 06:18.944
ANYTIME THEY'RE WITH YOU.

06:18.946 --> 06:21.980
SURELY YOU WANT THEM
TO HAVE SOME PROTECTION.

06:21.982 --> 06:25.917
WELL,
IT CAN'T HURT, CAN IT?

06:29.890 --> 06:31.857
FINE.

06:31.859 --> 06:32.958
YOU WIN.

06:38.599 --> 06:40.699
[ DOOR OPENS ]

06:44.071 --> 06:46.405
<i> NEW DEVELOPMENTS</i>
<i> IN THE KIDNAPPING</i>

06:46.407 --> 06:47.506
<i> OF SARAH THOMPSON</i>
<i> HAVE EMERGED --</i>

06:47.508 --> 06:48.974
[ TV SHUTS OFF ]

06:48.976 --> 06:50.442
I WASN'T WATCHING THAT.

06:50.444 --> 06:52.878
WHY ARE THE COPS OUTSIDE?

06:52.880 --> 06:54.780
I ASKED FOR A DETAIL.

06:54.782 --> 06:56.948
A DETAIL?

06:56.950 --> 06:58.083
WHAT?
LIKE, TO PROTECT US?

06:58.085 --> 07:00.585
YEAH,
KEEP AN EYE ON THINGS.

07:00.587 --> 07:02.087
WHY NOW?

07:02.089 --> 07:03.488
IT'S GONNA BE FINE.

07:03.490 --> 07:05.957
YOU KNOW I'M NOT ABBY,
RIGHT?

07:05.959 --> 07:08.760
OKAY, HON.
MY TRUCK WAS TAMPERED WITH.

07:08.762 --> 07:10.929
AND AFTER THE FLASHLIGHTS
IN THE GARAGE,

07:10.931 --> 07:12.998
WE JUST WANT TO MAKE SURE
NOTHING ELSE HAPPENS.

07:13.000 --> 07:15.033
WHAT COULD HAPPEN?
NOTHING.

07:16.437 --> 07:18.904
I ASKED FOR THEM.

07:18.906 --> 07:20.472
THEY'RE JUST BEING CAREFUL.

07:20.474 --> 07:22.090
[ BOTTLES CLINK ]

07:22.091 --> 07:23.707
YOU DO REALIZE YOU DON'T
LIVE HERE ANYMORE, RIGHT?

07:23.710 --> 07:25.644
I'M VISITING.

07:25.646 --> 07:27.212
[ BOTTLE CAP CLINKS ]
BY THE WAY,
YOUR SECURITY SUCKS.

07:27.214 --> 07:29.948
Natalie:
DAD, WHAT'S REALLY GOING ON?

07:29.950 --> 07:30.849
HONEY --

07:30.851 --> 07:32.117
WORRY NOT, YOUNG ONE.

07:32.119 --> 07:34.820
THE PSYCHO VIGILANTE
IS AFTER YOUR POPS, NOT YOU.

07:34.822 --> 07:38.123
NO ONE ASKED YOU,
AND NO ONE'S AFTER ME.

07:38.125 --> 07:39.558
NO, THANK YOU, DAVE.

07:39.560 --> 07:42.227
IT'S NICE TO BE TREATED
LIKE AN ADULT.

07:43.964 --> 07:44.963
SORRY.

07:44.965 --> 07:46.865
[ TV CHATTER ]

07:46.866 --> 07:48.766
I'LL KEEP MY MOUTH SHUT
FROM NOW ON.

07:48.769 --> 07:50.001
CAN YOU?

07:50.003 --> 07:50.969
[ SIGHS ]

07:50.971 --> 07:52.237
HAVEN'T SEEN
HER BROOMSTICK.

07:52.239 --> 07:53.905
[ BOTTLES CLINK ]

07:53.907 --> 07:57.075
WHERE IS
SHE WHO MUST NOT BE NAMED?

07:57.077 --> 07:58.877
Christy:
WORKING IN MY OFFICE.

07:58.879 --> 08:02.647
HEY, CHRISTY.
YOU LOOK GREAT.

08:04.918 --> 08:06.918
[ CELLPHONE RINGING, VIBRATING ]

08:06.920 --> 08:08.053
[ BEEP ]

08:21.768 --> 08:23.768
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

08:23.770 --> 08:25.270
Dave:<i> ...KNOW IF THE FLASHLIGHT</i>
<i> IS THE MURDER WEAPON.</i>

08:25.272 --> 08:28.073
Ben:<i> I'M NOT STUPID.</i>
<i> I WIPED IT OFF.</i>

08:28.075 --> 08:29.074
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

08:29.076 --> 08:30.742
<i> IT'S CALLED TAMPERING.</i>

08:30.744 --> 08:32.711
THAT'S ME.
<i> FELONY.</i>

08:32.713 --> 08:33.945
<i>GOT TO GET RID OF IT.</i>

08:33.947 --> 08:35.247
<i> HOW?</i>

08:35.249 --> 08:37.682
<i>IF THEY'RE WATCHING ME...</i>
WHAT THE HELL?

08:37.684 --> 08:38.784
<i> ...MURDER WEAPON.</i>

08:38.785 --> 08:39.885
<i> I'LL DO IT.</i>
<i> I'LL GET RID OF IT.</i>

08:39.887 --> 08:41.219
<i>IT'S IN A SAFE PLACE.</i>

08:41.221 --> 08:43.121
<i> YOU'RE SURE?</i>

08:43.123 --> 08:45.924
WHO --
WHO SENT THIS TO YOU?

08:45.926 --> 08:48.793
IT SAYS I DID.

08:48.795 --> 08:50.295
OKAY, THAT'S NOT GOOD.

08:50.297 --> 08:52.764
WE GOT TO TELL CORNELL,
MAN.

08:52.766 --> 08:54.933
AND PLAY THAT FOR HER?

08:56.703 --> 08:59.004
How did they record us?

09:00.173 --> 09:04.643
THEY HAD TO
PLANT EQUIPMENT.

09:04.645 --> 09:06.978
[ DOOR OPENS ]

09:06.980 --> 09:09.214
THIS IS CRAZY.

09:09.216 --> 09:12.284
THIS IS CRAZY.

09:12.286 --> 09:14.019
SO CREEPY.

09:15.155 --> 09:16.988
FREAKING OUT HERE, MAN.

09:16.990 --> 09:19.991
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

09:19.993 --> 09:22.761
IT'S LIKE
THE GUY'S EVERYWHERE.

09:22.763 --> 09:25.864
CAMERAS, MICROPHONES.

09:25.866 --> 09:27.966
IT'S LIKE "1984."

09:32.039 --> 09:35.106
HERE WE GO.

09:35.108 --> 09:36.875
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

09:36.877 --> 09:38.977
HMM.

09:38.979 --> 09:40.946
IT'S AN X37 COVERT CAM.

09:40.948 --> 09:42.213
MILITARY GRADE.

09:42.215 --> 09:44.215
OH, MY GOD.

09:44.217 --> 09:45.817
HOW DID YOU KNOW
IT WOULD BE HERE?

09:45.819 --> 09:47.953
SOMEONE'S
BEEN WATCHING ME.

09:47.955 --> 09:49.120
THEY HAD TO
BE DOING IT SOMEHOW.

09:49.122 --> 09:51.823
SO YOU JUST
FIGURED IT OUT?

09:51.825 --> 09:53.325
YES.

09:54.261 --> 09:55.994
ARE THERE OTHERS?

09:55.996 --> 09:59.831
THE ONLY WAY FOR US TO KNOW
IS TO SEARCH YOUR WHOLE HOUSE.

10:01.335 --> 10:04.002
THE DETAIL'S ASSIGNED
TO MY WIFE AND KIDS.

10:04.004 --> 10:04.970
YEAH.

10:04.972 --> 10:06.738
AND YOU'LL KEEP THEM SAFE?

10:06.740 --> 10:08.006
I WILL.

10:08.842 --> 10:09.874
THEN SEARCH AWAY.

10:09.876 --> 10:12.344
I WON'T BE HERE.

10:13.714 --> 10:16.114
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

10:18.218 --> 10:20.318
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

10:24.791 --> 10:26.691
DAVE'S.
WHAT?

10:26.693 --> 10:28.960
YEAH, THEY'LL SEARCH THE HOUSE
AND FIND ANY OTHER CAMERAS

10:28.962 --> 10:30.895
OR ANYTHING THIS GUY'S USING
TO STALK ME.

10:30.897 --> 10:32.897
SO, WHY CAN'T YOU STAY?

10:32.898 --> 10:34.898
YOU GUYS WILL HAVE THE DETAIL.
YOU'LL BE SAFE.

10:34.901 --> 10:36.334
BUT HE'S AFTER YOU.

10:36.336 --> 10:38.103
I'M NOT GONNA LET COPS
FOLLOW ME AROUND.

10:38.105 --> 10:39.237
WHY? WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA BE DOING?

10:39.239 --> 10:40.672
WHY ARE THEY HERE
AGAIN?

10:40.674 --> 10:43.041
[ SIGHS ] SORRY. I TRIED
TO KEEP HER UPSTAIRS.

10:43.043 --> 10:45.944
I'M NOT A BABY.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

10:45.946 --> 10:47.979
HONEY, THE POLICE ARE HERE
TO KEEP US SAFE. THAT'S ALL.

10:47.981 --> 10:48.980
FROM WHO?

10:50.117 --> 10:51.883
LISTEN, MONKEY.

10:51.885 --> 10:57.022
SOMEONE IS MAD AT DAD
AND DOING SOME CRAZY STUFF.

10:57.024 --> 10:59.057
I'M AFRAID
THAT IF HE COMES AFTER ME

10:59.059 --> 11:00.358
AND I'M WITH YOU GUYS,

11:00.360 --> 11:03.028
YOU WOULD GET HURT,
AND THAT CAN'T HAPPEN.

11:03.030 --> 11:04.896
SO, I NEED YOU
TO STAY HERE

11:04.898 --> 11:06.898
WITH YOUR SISTER AND MOTHER,
AND BE STRONG.

11:06.900 --> 11:07.966
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

11:07.968 --> 11:09.067
I'M GONNA GO STAY
WITH DAVE

11:09.069 --> 11:10.769
UNTIL THE COPS
FIGURE THIS OUT.

11:10.771 --> 11:12.904
I COULD TAKE THEM
TO MICHAEL'S.

11:12.906 --> 11:14.806
NO. MICHAEL LIVES
IN ANOTHER COUNTY.

11:14.808 --> 11:17.008
NO.
DETAIL WON'T EXTEND THERE.

11:18.345 --> 11:20.945
YOU GUYS,
I'M GONNA BE OKAY.

11:20.947 --> 11:22.113
YOU PROMISE?

11:22.115 --> 11:24.115
PROMISE.

11:24.117 --> 11:26.117
YOU CAN'T PROMISE THAT.

11:30.724 --> 11:32.891
[ SIGHS ]
CAN I HAVE A HUG?

11:35.028 --> 11:36.961
IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.

11:36.963 --> 11:38.396
BE CAREFUL.

11:40.967 --> 11:42.901
[ DOOR OPENS ]

11:42.903 --> 11:45.270
AWESOME.
TOTAL BACHELOR PAD.

11:45.272 --> 11:46.938
SO, WAIT.
IT'S ON McLAREN?

11:46.940 --> 11:48.873
YEAH, IT'S AT THE END
THE BLOCK THERE.

11:48.875 --> 11:50.775
IT'S THE KIND OF
GRAYISH-TONED ONE.

11:51.311 --> 11:53.211
HEY.
HEY.

11:53.213 --> 11:54.946
LET'S GO.
OKAY.

11:54.948 --> 11:56.281
HEY,
WHERE'S YOUR TRUCK?

11:56.283 --> 11:57.849
OH, IT'S IN THE SHOP.

11:57.851 --> 11:59.150
YOU GUYS GOING
ON A TRIP?

11:59.152 --> 12:01.486
JUST GONNA GO STAY
WITH DAVE.

12:01.488 --> 12:04.289
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]
OH.
UH, BEN, I'M SO SORRY.

12:04.291 --> 12:06.057
WHAT?

12:06.059 --> 12:08.827
I MEAN,
IS -- IS IT MY FAULT?

12:10.464 --> 12:12.197
NO.
[ SCOFFS ]

12:12.199 --> 12:13.998
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

12:15.869 --> 12:17.335
Dave: YOU READY?

12:17.337 --> 12:18.837
I AM NOW.

12:18.839 --> 12:20.371
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

12:24.945 --> 12:27.212
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

12:35.789 --> 12:38.289
YOU'RE GONNA LOVE IT HERE.
YOU WANT YOUR CHANGE?

12:38.291 --> 12:39.357
CAN I HAVE IT?

12:39.359 --> 12:41.059
YES.
REALLY?

12:41.061 --> 12:42.460
YEAH.
THANK YOU.

12:42.462 --> 12:45.897
[ SIGHS ]

12:45.899 --> 12:47.499
SO, YOU THINK, UH,

12:47.501 --> 12:50.168
CORNELL'S GOING THROUGH
YOUR UNDERPANTS RIGHT NOW?

12:50.170 --> 12:53.872
AS LONG AS MY FAMILY'S SAFE,
I DON'T CARE WHAT SHE'S DOING.

12:53.874 --> 12:56.040
WISH SHE WAS GOING THROUGH
<i>MY</i> UNDERPANTS RIGHT NOW.

12:56.042 --> 12:59.778
YOU KNOW, I, UH,
WAS THINKING,

12:59.780 --> 13:02.113
IF SHE'S GOING THROUGH
ALL YOUR STUFF,

13:02.115 --> 13:04.516
AREN'T YOU WORRIED ABOUT
THE ashlight-flay?

13:04.518 --> 13:05.984
UH,
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

13:05.986 --> 13:08.453
BUT I WAS, UH --
I WAS THINKING ABOUT,

13:08.455 --> 13:12.791
LIKE,
WHAT WOULD I DO, YOU KNOW?

13:12.793 --> 13:16.094
IF I HAD TO GET RID
OF A MURDER WEAPON,

13:16.096 --> 13:18.930
WHERE WOULD I GET RID OF IT,
HYPOTHETICALLY?

13:18.932 --> 13:20.064
HYPOTHETICALLY?

13:20.066 --> 13:21.833
YEAH.

13:21.835 --> 13:23.268
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

13:23.270 --> 13:26.137
ANYWAYS, ON THE WAY
TO YOUR ASSHAT BROTHER-IN-LAW'S

13:26.139 --> 13:30.275
FOR HIS ANNUAL, UH, LAME PARTY
THAT HE NEVER INVITES ME TO,

13:30.277 --> 13:32.210
IT'S 20 MILES OF WOODS.

13:32.212 --> 13:33.244
THERE'S NOTHING.

13:33.246 --> 13:36.080
IT'S LIKE NO TRAILS,

13:36.082 --> 13:38.666
UNCHARTED TERRITORY
TO YOU.

13:38.667 --> 13:41.251
AND "48 HOURS" SAYS
THAT IF YOU WANTED TO, YOU KNOW,

13:41.254 --> 13:44.022
HIDE SOMETHING,
NEVER WANT IT FOUND,

13:44.024 --> 13:45.190
THAT'S A REALLY GOOD PLACE
TO DO IT.

13:45.192 --> 13:46.825
I'LL KEEP THAT IN MIND

13:46.827 --> 13:48.927
WHEN I HAVE CHRISTY
AND THE GIRLS IN THE CAR.

13:48.929 --> 13:51.062
JUST SAYING.

13:51.064 --> 13:52.363
HEY, THAT'S MINE.

13:54.034 --> 13:55.266
WORLD'S GREATEST DAD.

13:55.268 --> 13:57.368
YOU LIVE LIKE THIS?

13:57.370 --> 13:59.537
CHICKS DIG IT, MAN.
IT'S BOHEMIAN.

13:59.539 --> 14:02.006
IT'S SAD.

14:02.008 --> 14:03.041
WHY?

14:03.043 --> 14:04.843
CHRISTY FELL FOR IT
WITH YOU.

14:04.845 --> 14:06.611
YEAH.
THAT WAS A LONG TIME AGO.

14:06.613 --> 14:08.012
HER TASTES HAVE CHANGED.

14:08.014 --> 14:10.915
YEAH,<i> SHE'S</i> CHANGED.

14:10.917 --> 14:12.917
[ CUP THUDS ]

14:12.919 --> 14:14.919
[ SIGHS ]

14:14.921 --> 14:16.421
WHAT HAPPENED TO HER?

14:18.091 --> 14:22.260
ONE DAY, IT WAS JUST LIKE
SHE WAS DIFFERENT, YOU KNOW?

14:22.262 --> 14:25.630
I'M NOT SURE WHEN.
MAYBE FOUR, FIVE YEARS AGO.

14:25.632 --> 14:27.966
[ DOOR OPENS ]
I'M PRETTY SURE IT WAS SIX.

14:27.968 --> 14:29.968
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

14:29.970 --> 14:33.004
[ CHRISTY SNIFFLES ]

14:33.006 --> 14:35.306
YOU DID IT, DIDN'T YOU?

14:38.278 --> 14:39.811
I MADE A CHOICE.

14:43.516 --> 14:46.317
I CAN'T EVEN LOOK AT YOU
RIGHT NOW.

14:48.355 --> 14:50.889
YOU WON'T HAVE TO.

14:50.891 --> 14:54.959
I'M TAKING THE GIRLS
TO MICHAEL'S.

14:54.961 --> 14:56.961
[ DOOR OPENS ]

14:56.963 --> 14:58.296
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

14:58.298 --> 14:59.530
Dave:
CHRISTY HAD AN ABORTION?

14:59.532 --> 15:02.333
WOW.

15:02.335 --> 15:05.970
BUDDY.

15:05.972 --> 15:07.972
YOU COULD HAVE TOLD ME.

15:09.042 --> 15:11.109
SHE MADE A DECISION.
WHAT'S LEFT TO SAY?

15:11.111 --> 15:14.045
I DON'T KNOW.
COULD'VE BEEN MAD WITH YOU.

15:14.047 --> 15:17.048
I DIDN'T WANT TO BE MAD.

15:17.050 --> 15:18.449
TELLING YOU
WASN'T GONNA HELP.

15:18.451 --> 15:22.020
I JUST NEEDED TO GET OVER IT
ON MY OWN.

15:22.022 --> 15:23.054
AND DID YOU?

15:24.190 --> 15:25.590
DID I WHAT?

15:25.592 --> 15:28.559
GET OVER IT?

15:28.561 --> 15:30.628
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS
IN DISTANCE ]

15:40.941 --> 15:43.007
[ MICHAEL FRANTI & SPEARHEAD'S
"SAY HEY (I LOVE YOU)" PLAYS ]

15:51.451 --> 15:54.686
¶ I LOVE YOU, I LOVE YOU,
I LOVE YOU ¶

15:56.356 --> 15:58.489
¶ I'VE BEEN A LOT OF PLACES
ALL AROUND THE WAY ¶

15:58.491 --> 16:01.225
¶ I'VE SEEN A LOT OF JOY,
AND I'VE SEEN A LOT OF PAIN ¶
[ KEVIN LAUGHS ]

16:01.227 --> 16:03.194
HEY, BEN.
KEV.

16:03.196 --> 16:05.964
TOSS THOSE IN THE COOLER
AND COME HAVE A DOG.

16:05.966 --> 16:07.499
OH, I'M NOT GONNA STAY, KEV.

16:07.500 --> 16:09.033
I'M JUST COMING BY TO SAY HI,
BE NEIGHBORLY.

16:09.035 --> 16:11.102
I SAW CHRISTY
AND THE GIRLS LEAVE.

16:11.104 --> 16:12.370
THEY HAVE OTHER PLANS?

16:13.206 --> 16:14.305
HEY, LOOK, COME ON.

16:14.307 --> 16:15.490
COME HANG OUT A WHILE

16:15.491 --> 16:16.674
AND HAVE A FEW DRINKS
AND FOOD,

16:16.676 --> 16:17.742
SEE THE ROCKETS'
RED GLARE.

16:17.744 --> 16:20.611
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:20.613 --> 16:22.113
[ LAUGHS ]
ALL RIGHT.

16:22.115 --> 16:24.015
¶ IT SEEMS LIKE
EVERYWHERE I GO ¶

16:24.017 --> 16:25.183
HEY, GUYS.

16:25.185 --> 16:26.985
¶ THE MORE I SEE,
THE LESS I KNOW ¶

16:26.987 --> 16:29.087
¶ BUT I KNOW ONE THING ¶

16:29.089 --> 16:30.421
¶ THAT I LOVE YOU ¶

16:30.423 --> 16:32.090
HEY.

16:32.092 --> 16:33.424
HI.

16:33.426 --> 16:35.593
¶ I LOVE YOU, I LOVE YOU ¶

16:35.595 --> 16:39.063
[ CAN OPENS ]
SO, YOUR FIRST 4th OF JULY
ON CHELSEA BAY DRIVE.

16:39.065 --> 16:40.698
YEAH, I DON'T KNOW
IF I CAN HANDLE IT, MAN.

16:40.700 --> 16:42.667
[ LAUGHS ]

16:42.669 --> 16:45.770
NO, IT'S, UH --
ACTUALLY, IT'S KIND OF NICE.

16:45.772 --> 16:47.105
IT'S LIKE
A REAL NEIGHBORHOOD.

16:47.107 --> 16:49.440
WHERE DID YOU LIVE BEFORE?
BASE HOUSING.

16:49.442 --> 16:51.442
YEAH, ARMY WIVES
ARE JUST REALLY NOSY.

16:51.444 --> 16:53.144
EVERYBODY STAYS
IN EACH OTHER'S BUSINESS.

16:53.146 --> 16:54.645
[ FIREWORKS CRACKLING ]

16:54.647 --> 16:56.781
OH, SO NOBODY WARNED YOU
ABOUT THESE PEOPLE.

16:56.783 --> 16:58.149
OH. [ LAUGHS ]

16:58.151 --> 17:01.085
HEY, WHERE'S, UH --
SCOTT.

17:01.087 --> 17:03.121
I THOUGHT HE WAS BACK.

17:03.123 --> 17:06.357
HE MADE THE CALL
TO STAY WITH HIS UNIT
A FEW WEEKS LONGER.

17:07.427 --> 17:09.193
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]
HIS GUYS COME FIRST.

17:10.163 --> 17:12.764
WHERE'S YOUR FAMILY?

17:12.766 --> 17:15.233
THEY WENT TO THE BEACH
FOR THE WEEKEND.

17:15.235 --> 17:17.402
WITHOUT YOU?

17:17.404 --> 17:19.170
I HAVE TO WORK.

17:19.172 --> 17:22.306
AW. NO ONE SHOULD BE ALONE
ON A HOLIDAY.

17:24.577 --> 17:26.177
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:26.179 --> 17:27.578
Dave: THEN THAT'S WHEN
YOU AND JESS...

17:29.282 --> 17:31.749
IT WAS STUPID.
I WAS PISSED OFF.

17:31.751 --> 17:33.518
ANGRY SEX.

17:33.520 --> 17:36.654
MUST HAVE BEEN INTENSE.

17:42.362 --> 17:46.531
AS MUCH AS I LOVE TOM...
I WISH IT NEVER HAPPENED.

17:46.533 --> 17:49.367
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

17:49.369 --> 17:50.501
[ CHOPSTICKS CLINK ]

17:50.503 --> 17:53.204
Grab the baseball bat.

17:55.442 --> 17:57.175
[ DOOR OPENS ]

17:58.344 --> 18:00.745
HELLO.

18:00.747 --> 18:03.381
COME ON IN.

18:05.785 --> 18:07.485
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

18:07.487 --> 18:09.454
I WANTED TO MAKE SURE
YOU'RE OKAY.

18:09.456 --> 18:10.822
I'M FINE.

18:11.758 --> 18:13.591
UH, DAVE,
CAN YOU GIVE US --

18:13.593 --> 18:18.830
YEAH, UH, I'LL BE, UH --
I'M GOING TO LEAVE NOW.

18:18.832 --> 18:21.799
I FEEL BAD.

18:21.801 --> 18:23.868
I MEAN, I --
CHRISTY THREW YOU OUT,

18:23.870 --> 18:25.303
AND I'M PARTLY
RESPONSIBLE.

18:25.305 --> 18:26.604
CHRISTY
DIDN'T THROW ME OUT,

18:26.606 --> 18:28.139
AND YOU HAVE NOTHING
TO DO WITH IT.

18:28.141 --> 18:29.607
[ SIGHS ]

18:29.609 --> 18:32.343
WHY ARE YOU HERE?
WE'RE FRIENDS.

18:32.345 --> 18:35.179
AND YOU'VE ALWAYS
BEEN THERE FOR ME, SO I JUST --

18:35.181 --> 18:36.314
I DON'T KNOW.
I THOUGHT THAT --

18:36.316 --> 18:41.152
THOUGHT WE'D HAVE A DRINK,
AND THEN WHAT?

18:42.856 --> 18:47.158
JESS, I KNOW YOU'RE SAD.
I'M -- I'M SAD, TOO.

18:47.160 --> 18:48.626
BUT MY FAMILY'S
FALLING APART.

18:48.628 --> 18:50.428
I GOT SOMEBODY
STALKING ME.

18:50.429 --> 18:52.229
I'M THE MAIN SUSPECT
IN OUR SON'S MURDER,

18:52.232 --> 18:55.199
SO FORGIVE ME IF I CAN'T
DEAL WITH THIS RIGHT NOW,

18:55.201 --> 18:57.435
BUT I JUST CAN'T.

18:57.437 --> 18:59.837
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

18:59.839 --> 19:01.906
[ SIGHS ]

19:04.677 --> 19:06.961
SORRY, MAN.

19:06.962 --> 19:09.246
DON'T APOLOGIZE TO ME, MAN.
SHE'S GOT NO ONE.

19:09.249 --> 19:10.381
JESS!

19:11.851 --> 19:13.918
[ CAR DOOR OPENS, CLOSES,
ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

19:13.920 --> 19:16.320
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

19:28.234 --> 19:30.234
[ GUN COCKS ]

19:30.236 --> 19:32.170
Kevin: STOP.

19:33.773 --> 19:35.306
MOVE. TO THE CAR.

19:35.308 --> 19:36.841
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

19:42.749 --> 19:44.282
[ CAR ALARM BEEPS ]

19:44.284 --> 19:46.217
GET IN.

19:49.522 --> 19:51.856
GET...IN.

19:57.597 --> 19:59.463
[ TRUNK LID CLOSES ]

20:03.703 --> 20:05.770
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

20:09.976 --> 20:13.411
¶ DO I REALLY WANT TO KNOW ¶

20:13.413 --> 20:15.880
¶ WHAT IT'S LIKE TO BE ¶

20:15.882 --> 20:17.848
[ Muffled ] ¶ ALL ALONE
AT THE TOP OF THE FOOD CHAIN? ¶

20:17.850 --> 20:20.384
[ Loudly ]
¶ LIVING UP TO STANDARDS ¶

20:20.386 --> 20:22.687
¶ IN FRONT OF CAMERAS ¶

20:22.689 --> 20:23.921
[ Muffled ] ¶ A THOUSAND EYES
STARING AT YOU ¶

20:23.923 --> 20:25.940
¶ HOPING YOU FALL ¶

20:25.941 --> 20:27.958
[ Loudly ]
¶ I WAS MADE FOR THIS ¶

20:28.995 --> 20:30.928
¶ I HEARD THE SOUND OF GLORY
CALLING ¶

20:30.930 --> 20:33.231
¶ AND I COULDN'T RESIST ¶

20:34.267 --> 20:36.334
¶ FROM WHAT I'VE LEARNED ¶

20:36.336 --> 20:37.868
[ MUFFLED MUSIC CONTINUES ]

20:37.870 --> 20:39.337
[ PEN SCRIBBLING ]

20:48.581 --> 20:50.948
[ BALL THUDDING ]

21:03.663 --> 21:04.996
[ Loudly ]
¶ BETTER SAVE YOURSELF ¶

21:04.998 --> 21:06.931
¶ WHEN DID IT START? ¶

21:06.933 --> 21:08.799
¶ LET ME BEGIN ¶

21:08.801 --> 21:11.502
¶ CHAPTER ONE,
PAGE ONE, ARE YOU -- ¶

21:11.504 --> 21:13.804
[ HEADPHONES CLATTER ]

21:19.812 --> 21:21.646
[ SCREAMING ]

21:21.648 --> 21:23.948
KEVIN, STOP!

21:23.950 --> 21:25.316
[ GRUNTS ]

21:25.318 --> 21:27.885
OH! OH!
KEVIN, PLEASE STOP!

21:27.887 --> 21:29.420
[ GASPING ]

21:34.494 --> 21:36.427
YOU GOT IT ALL WRONG!

21:36.429 --> 21:39.497
[ PANTING ]

21:39.499 --> 21:41.866
PLEASE LISTEN!

21:41.868 --> 21:44.635
I DIDN'T -- [ GRUNTING ]

21:46.606 --> 21:48.839
[ GASPING ]

21:48.841 --> 21:52.376
[ PANTING ]

21:52.378 --> 21:54.462
KEVIN.

21:54.463 --> 21:56.547
YOU THINK I KILLED [GASPS] TOM.
IT'S JUST NOT TRUE.

22:02.522 --> 22:05.456
COLD. AMAZING.

22:05.458 --> 22:06.791
IT'S BLISTERING
DURING THE DAY,

22:06.793 --> 22:08.492
BUT THE TEMPERATURE
REALLY COMES DOWN AT NIGHT,

22:08.494 --> 22:11.028
ESPECIALLY
ALL THE WAY OUT HERE.

22:11.030 --> 22:13.764
[ BREATHING SHAKILY ]

22:20.907 --> 22:21.906
[ GRUNTS ]

22:21.908 --> 22:23.007
LET'S GET
THOSE WET CLOTHES OFF.

22:27.714 --> 22:29.847
[ FABRIC TEARING ]

22:40.593 --> 22:43.661
YOU KNOW I SERVED
IN THE FIRST GULF WAR.

22:43.663 --> 22:45.696
YOU KNOW I WORKED
FOR THE STATE DEPARTMENT

22:45.698 --> 22:47.598
AND WAS GONE
FOR LONG PERIODS OF TIME.

22:47.600 --> 22:50.835
EVER WONDER
WHAT I WAS DOING?

22:52.805 --> 22:54.638
I'VE BEEN IN PLACES
LIKE THIS

22:54.640 --> 22:57.742
WITH PEOPLE LIKE YOU
[SIGHS] HUNDREDS OF TIME.

22:57.744 --> 22:58.976
I'M NOT TRYING TO BOAST.

22:58.978 --> 23:01.312
I JUST WANT TO ALLAY
ANY CONCERNS YOU MAY HAVE

23:01.314 --> 23:02.913
THAT I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I'M DOING.

23:04.684 --> 23:07.618
I JUST NEED TO START
BY ASKING YOU A FEW QUESTIONS.

23:10.523 --> 23:12.857
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
YOU SLEPT?

23:12.859 --> 23:14.909
WHAT?

23:14.910 --> 23:16.960
SIMPLE QUESTION.
TRY NOT TO LIE.

23:16.963 --> 23:18.462
LAST NIGHT.

23:18.464 --> 23:19.797
FOR HOW LONG?

23:23.436 --> 23:25.970
KEVIN,
YOU'VE BEEN TO MY HOUSE.

23:25.972 --> 23:27.671
YOU KNOW CHRISTY.
YOU KNOW NATALIE.

23:27.673 --> 23:28.939
FORGET THEM.

23:30.676 --> 23:32.943
FORGET YOUR WORLD
AS YOU KNEW IT.

23:34.080 --> 23:36.647
HERE.

23:36.649 --> 23:37.882
NOW.

23:37.884 --> 23:40.951
THIS IS YOUR WORLD.

23:43.489 --> 23:46.157
I ASK...

23:46.159 --> 23:47.792
YOU ANSWER.

23:47.794 --> 23:51.529
YOU LIE...I PUNISH.

23:51.531 --> 23:53.831
I DIDN'T KILL TOM!

23:53.833 --> 23:57.902
I ASK, YOU ANSWER.

23:58.971 --> 24:01.906
OHH!

24:01.908 --> 24:04.809
[ GROANS ]

24:04.811 --> 24:06.544
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?!

24:06.546 --> 24:11.449
I ASK, YOU ANSWER.

24:11.451 --> 24:12.716
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

24:12.718 --> 24:14.752
[ INHALES SHAKILY ]

24:14.754 --> 24:17.221
YES.
I UNDERSTAND.

24:17.223 --> 24:18.556
THEN WE CAN BEGIN.

24:20.693 --> 24:23.894
I'LL START WITH QUESTIONS
TO WHICH I KNOW THE ANSWER.

24:23.896 --> 24:28.065
THIS WILL GET YOU IN THE HABIT
OF BEING TRUTHFUL.

24:34.907 --> 24:36.140
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

24:41.981 --> 24:43.247
RIVER WATER.

24:44.717 --> 24:46.684
IF YOU DIE DURING QUESTIONING,

24:46.686 --> 24:48.152
I SIMPLY DUMP YOU
OFF THE BRIDGE.

24:48.154 --> 24:50.171
WHAT'S THE TOWEL FOR?

24:50.172 --> 24:52.189
THE WATER IN YOUR LUNGS
WOULD BE CONSISTENT
WITH ACCIDENTAL DROWNING.

24:52.191 --> 24:56.694
OR, GIVEN THE CIRCUMSTANCES,
THE COPS THINK SUICIDE.

24:56.696 --> 24:58.496
CASE CLOSED.

24:58.498 --> 25:00.564
KEVIN, YOU DON'T WANT
TO DO THIS.

25:02.502 --> 25:04.101
WHEN DID I STOP LIKING YOU?

25:04.103 --> 25:05.569
I DON'T KNOW.

25:05.571 --> 25:07.938
"I DON'T KNOW" IS NOT
AN ACCEPTABLE ANSWER.

25:07.940 --> 25:09.006
I FORGOT TO TELL YOU.
MY MISTAKE.

25:09.008 --> 25:10.674
SORRY.

25:11.844 --> 25:16.947
[ MUFFLED SCREAMS,
COUGHING ]

25:20.686 --> 25:22.920
WHEN DID I STOP LIKING YOU?

25:22.922 --> 25:24.989
[ GASPING ]

25:29.862 --> 25:31.662
FIVE OR SIX YEARS AGO.

25:31.664 --> 25:33.631
THIS ISN'T MULTIPLE CHOICE.
WHICH IS IT? FIVE OR SIX.

25:33.633 --> 25:35.199
WHY DOES IT MATTER?
WHAT MONTH?

25:35.201 --> 25:37.034
I DON'T KNOW!

25:38.137 --> 25:41.038
[ SHOUTS ]

25:41.040 --> 25:42.940
UH, SEPTEMBER.

25:43.976 --> 25:45.676
I WAS OUT OF TOWN
ALL OF AUGUST.

25:45.678 --> 25:47.945
WHAT HAPPENED SIX YEARS AGO
IN JULY?

25:47.947 --> 25:50.648
THE 4th.

25:50.650 --> 25:51.982
INDEPENDENCE DAY.

25:51.984 --> 25:53.717
[ MUSIC PLAYING ON STEREO ]
I'M STARVING RIGHT NOW.

25:53.719 --> 25:56.287
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M ACTUALLY REALLY HUNGRY.

25:56.289 --> 25:58.589
Ben: WELL, KEVIN DOES
THIS 12-HOUR STEAK.

25:58.591 --> 25:59.740
MM-HMM?

25:59.741 --> 26:00.890
[ CHUCKLES ] IS THAT
WHAT'S GOING ON RIGHT NOW?

26:00.893 --> 26:02.960
YEAH.

26:02.961 --> 26:05.028
HEY, KEV, HOW'S IT GOING
WITH THOSE STEAKS?

26:05.031 --> 26:08.198
I THINK, UH, JESS MIGHT TURN
ON US IF SHE DOESN'T EAT SOON.
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:08.200 --> 26:09.833
Kevin:
UH, ALMOST READY.

26:09.835 --> 26:11.869
I JUST WISH I HAD
A LITTLE MORE CHARCOAL.

26:11.871 --> 26:14.805
I HAVE SOME.
I'LL GO GET IT.

26:14.807 --> 26:16.774
OKAY, GREAT.
GREAT. GREAT.

26:16.776 --> 26:18.776
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES,
MUSIC STOPS ]

26:18.778 --> 26:20.444
Elaine: OH, I THINK --

26:20.445 --> 26:22.111
I THINK THIS, UM,
EXTENSION CORD IS FRIED.

26:22.114 --> 26:24.048
BEN?

26:24.850 --> 26:26.216
OH, DO YOU WANT ME TO SEE
IF HE HAS ANOTHER?

26:26.218 --> 26:27.585
YES, PLEASE.

26:27.587 --> 26:29.019
YEAH.

26:29.021 --> 26:31.355
STILL CAN'T SEE
WHAT'S RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOU.

26:31.357 --> 26:33.123
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

26:33.125 --> 26:37.027
THE SAME SELFISH, SELF-CENTERED
WAY YOU SEE EVERYTHING.

26:37.029 --> 26:39.029
IT'S ALL ABOUT BEN.

26:42.768 --> 26:44.668
E-ELAINE, SWEETHEART,
COVER THE GRILL FOR ME.

26:44.670 --> 26:46.904
BEN'S TAKING TOO LONG,
AND MY COALS ARE DYING.

26:46.906 --> 26:48.172
OKAY, NO PROBLEM.

26:48.174 --> 26:49.873
UH, LISTEN,
DON'T TOUCH ANYTHING.

26:49.875 --> 26:52.009
JUST WATCH IT.

26:52.011 --> 26:52.943
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:01.354 --> 27:03.621
BEN?

27:20.039 --> 27:22.806
Kevin:
YOU SCREWED A SOLDIER'S WIFE
WHILE HE WAS OFF PROTECTING

27:22.808 --> 27:26.410
THE FREEDOM YOU TAKE FOR GRANTED
EVERY SECOND OF YOUR LIFE.

27:26.412 --> 27:28.412
YOU KNEW THE WHOLE TIME?

27:28.414 --> 27:29.880
YES.

27:29.882 --> 27:33.083
I'VE BEEN ON TO YOU
FOR A WHILE.

27:33.085 --> 27:35.953
I WATCHED AND LISTENED.

27:35.955 --> 27:37.921
YEAH,
I FOUND YOUR CAMERA.

27:37.923 --> 27:39.323
GOOD FOR YOU.

27:39.325 --> 27:42.826
TOO BAD I CLONED YOUR CELL --
SENT A FEW TEXTS,

27:42.828 --> 27:45.996
TURNED ON THE MICROPHONE
WHENEVER I FELT LIKE IT,

27:45.998 --> 27:48.298
MADE DIGITAL FILES.

27:48.300 --> 27:50.367
WHY DIDN'T YOU JUST GIVE THEM
TO CORNELL?

27:50.369 --> 27:51.869
CORNELL ALREADY THINKS
YOU'RE A KILLER.

27:51.871 --> 27:54.071
WHY PUT MYSELF
IN THE HOT SEAT?

27:54.073 --> 27:56.774
I DIDN'T DO IT.

27:56.776 --> 27:59.043
YES.

27:59.045 --> 28:02.446
YOU DID.

28:02.447 --> 28:05.848
I KNOW WHO YOU ARE,
AND I KNOW YOU KILLED TOM.

28:05.851 --> 28:07.451
AND THAT'S HOW I KNOW

28:07.453 --> 28:11.321
YOU'RE GONNA CONFESS
BEFORE I'M THROUGH.

28:11.323 --> 28:13.223
[ PANTING ]

28:17.797 --> 28:19.697
[ COUGHING ]

28:19.699 --> 28:21.699
YOU OKAY?

28:21.701 --> 28:23.367
[ SNIFFS ]
IT WAS A MISTAKE!

28:23.369 --> 28:26.336
WE CAN TAKE A BREAK
IF YOU NEED IT.

28:27.973 --> 28:30.040
YOU'RE COLD.

28:30.042 --> 28:32.109
[ BREATHING SHAKILY ]

28:37.383 --> 28:38.816
BETTER?

28:41.987 --> 28:44.955
SO, TELL ME.

28:44.957 --> 28:47.458
HOW MANY TIMES DID YOU SCREW
THE SOLDIER'S WIFE?

28:47.460 --> 28:49.860
JUST ONCE.

28:49.862 --> 28:52.763
OHH! [ GRUNTS ]

28:52.765 --> 28:53.997
JUST ONCE?

28:53.999 --> 28:57.735
I-I SW-- I SWEAR!
IT'S THE TRUTH!

28:57.737 --> 28:59.903
AND YOU THINK IT'S OKAY
BECAUSE IT HAPPENED JUST ONCE?

29:01.173 --> 29:04.041
IT'S NOT.

29:04.043 --> 29:05.442
ALL RIGHT. THIS IS IT.

29:05.444 --> 29:07.377
ROOKIE TOM MURPHY LINES UP

29:07.379 --> 29:09.046
FOR THE GAME-WINNING
EXTRA POINT.

29:09.048 --> 29:10.781
THIS ONE'S GOING IN.
I CAN FEEL IT.

29:10.783 --> 29:12.750
IT ALL COMES DOWN
TO THIS.

29:12.752 --> 29:15.119
HERE WE GO.
READY?

29:15.121 --> 29:18.088
SET. HUT!

29:20.526 --> 29:22.025
Tom: YES!
WINNER!

29:22.027 --> 29:23.894
YEAH!

29:23.896 --> 29:25.229
GIVE ME FIVE.
YES!

29:25.231 --> 29:27.464
[ Chuckling ] GOOD JOB.
YOU WON!

29:27.466 --> 29:29.883
YOU WON THE GAME!

29:29.884 --> 29:32.301
Kevin: YOU SCREWED
A SOLDIER'S WIFE JUST ONCE,

29:32.304 --> 29:34.772
AND AFTER YOU DID,
HOW MUCH QUICKER

29:34.774 --> 29:36.974
DID JESS CALL ON YOU
TO SPEND TIME WITH TOM

29:36.976 --> 29:38.776
WHEN SHE SHOULD HAVE BEEN
REACHING OUT TO SCOTT?

29:38.778 --> 29:41.011
TOM WAS AT MY HOUSE
ALL THE TIME.

29:41.013 --> 29:42.045
WHAT SHOULD I HAVE DONE?

29:42.047 --> 29:44.414
SHOULD I JUST HAVE
IGNORED HIM?

29:44.416 --> 29:47.284
AND WHY NOT?

29:47.286 --> 29:49.219
YOU WERE
JUST ACROSS THE STREET

29:49.221 --> 29:51.922
WHILE HER HUSBAND WAS OFF
PROTECTING HIS COUNTRY,

29:51.924 --> 29:53.857
PROTECTING YOU.

29:56.796 --> 29:58.028
I DON'T BLAME HER.

29:58.030 --> 30:00.964
ELAINE WAS ALONE,
SCARED, VULNERABLE.

30:00.966 --> 30:02.966
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

30:02.968 --> 30:04.368
YOU TOOK ADVANTAGE
OF THAT.

30:06.972 --> 30:08.005
ELAINE?

30:08.007 --> 30:09.006
WHAT?

30:09.008 --> 30:10.240
YOU JUST SAID ELAINE.

30:10.242 --> 30:11.975
NO.
YES, YOU DID.

30:11.977 --> 30:15.012
YOU SAID
YOU DON'T BLAME ELAINE.

30:15.014 --> 30:16.547
FOR WHAT?

30:16.549 --> 30:18.916
WHAT DID SHE DO, KEVIN?

30:18.918 --> 30:20.417
DID IT HAPPEN
WHILE YOU WERE IN KUWAIT?

30:20.419 --> 30:22.452
DID SHE SCREW
SOMEBODY ELSE?

30:25.024 --> 30:26.590
I ASK!

30:26.592 --> 30:29.293
OHH!
YOU ANSWER!

30:33.032 --> 30:34.398
[ GRUNTS ]

30:34.400 --> 30:36.466
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

30:38.537 --> 30:40.604
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

30:44.343 --> 30:45.442
HEAR THAT?

30:45.444 --> 30:48.078
HEAR WHAT?

30:48.080 --> 30:49.913
THE PEOPLE.

30:49.915 --> 30:51.148
I DON'T HEAR ANYTHING.

30:51.150 --> 30:53.183
YOU DON'T HEAR
THE HIGHWAY?

30:53.185 --> 30:55.118
NO.

30:55.120 --> 30:56.954
OH. I KNOW WHY.

30:56.956 --> 30:58.121
BECAUSE THERE'S NO ONE
AND NOTHING

30:58.123 --> 31:01.124
FOR 15 MILES
IN EVERY DIRECTION.

31:05.030 --> 31:07.631
STOP.

31:13.639 --> 31:17.975
DID YOU KILL TOM MURPHY?

31:17.977 --> 31:19.109
NO.

31:20.479 --> 31:21.879
THEN DIG.

31:24.049 --> 31:25.916
IS THIS HOW YOU DID
ALL YOUR INTERROGATIONS?

31:25.918 --> 31:26.917
YES.

31:26.919 --> 31:28.619
[ SHOVEL CLATTERS ]

31:28.621 --> 31:30.921
ONLY THEY GOT TO USE
THE SHOVEL.

31:30.923 --> 31:33.190
DIG.

31:38.631 --> 31:40.898
YOU CAN STOP WHEN YOU'RE READY
TO TELL THE TRUTH

31:40.900 --> 31:42.132
ABOUT TOM'S MURDER.

31:44.904 --> 31:47.671
[ GRUNTS ]

31:57.016 --> 31:58.482
AH.

31:59.385 --> 32:00.617
DIG!

32:00.619 --> 32:02.686
[ COUGHS ]

32:09.061 --> 32:11.561
HUNDREDS OF INTERROGATIONS?

32:11.563 --> 32:13.096
SHUT UP.

32:13.098 --> 32:14.364
THAT'S A LOT.

32:14.366 --> 32:16.633
IF YOU'RE READY TO CONFESS,
OKAY.

32:16.635 --> 32:18.936
OTHERWISE...

32:18.938 --> 32:20.270
DIG.

32:20.272 --> 32:22.339
[ SIGHS ]

32:25.210 --> 32:30.380
OF THE HUNDREDS,
HOW MANY DID YOU TORTURE

32:30.382 --> 32:33.383
'CAUSE THEY REMINDED YOU OF
THE OTHER GUY YOUR WIFE SCREWED?

32:33.385 --> 32:34.584
[ GRUNTS ]

32:41.460 --> 32:43.360
[ BEEPING ]

33:05.417 --> 33:07.417
[ CELLPHONE BEEPING ]

33:25.771 --> 33:28.372
[ GUNSHOT ]

33:28.374 --> 33:30.674
[ CELLPHONE BEEPING ]
[ Ringing ]

33:30.676 --> 33:32.275
DISPATCHER:
911. What is the nature
of your emergency?

33:32.277 --> 33:35.112
THIS IS BEN CRAWFORD!
I NEED DETECTIVE CORNELL!

33:35.114 --> 33:36.313
Kevin: NOT MUCH OF A SIGNAL
OUT HERE, BEN.

33:36.315 --> 33:38.548
I NEED CORNELL!
Calm down.

33:38.550 --> 33:40.717
Please be clear and state
the nature of your emergency.

33:40.719 --> 33:43.086
BEN CRAWFORD.
I NEED --

33:43.088 --> 33:44.488
GIVE ME THE PHONE.

33:44.490 --> 33:47.357
Sir, what is the nature
of your emergency?

33:47.359 --> 33:50.227
Sir? Hello?

33:50.229 --> 33:52.763
Are you there?
Are you there?

33:52.765 --> 33:54.331
Sir?

34:00.039 --> 34:02.105
MOVE.

34:10.682 --> 34:12.749
[ SHOVEL SCRAPING ]

34:17.823 --> 34:21.124
THAT'S DEEP ENOUGH.

34:22.361 --> 34:24.628
YOU READY TO CONFESS?

34:26.231 --> 34:28.165
I DIDN'T
KILL TOM.

34:28.167 --> 34:30.367
LIE DOWN.

34:30.369 --> 34:32.102
NO.
[ SHOVEL CLATTERS ]

34:33.472 --> 34:35.105
SAY AGAIN?

34:35.107 --> 34:38.241
I PUT THIS IN YOUR MOUTH,
PULL THE TRIGGER,

34:38.243 --> 34:39.709
THE EXPANDING GASES
FROM THE BARREL

34:39.711 --> 34:42.179
EXPLODE YOUR HEAD
LIKE AN OVERRIPE MELON.

34:43.849 --> 34:45.182
DO YOU KNOW
HOW INSANE YOU ARE?

34:45.184 --> 34:46.516
YOU'RE THE BAD GUY,
NOT ME.

34:46.518 --> 34:48.485
IF I KILLED TOM,
YOU'RE RIGHT.

34:48.487 --> 34:49.853
BUT WHAT IF YOU'RE WRONG,
KEVIN?

34:49.855 --> 34:53.290
IF I DIDN'T DO IT,
WHAT'S THAT MAKE YOU?

34:56.328 --> 34:59.129
LAST CHANCE.

34:59.131 --> 35:00.263
ADMIT WHAT YOU DID.

35:00.265 --> 35:02.032
TELL THE TRUTH.

35:02.034 --> 35:03.633
YOU DON'T CARE
ABOUT THE TRUTH.

35:03.635 --> 35:05.218
I CARE DEEPLY ABOUT IT.

35:05.219 --> 35:06.802
THAT LITTLE BOY HAD
HIS WHOLE LIFE AHEAD OF HIM,

35:06.805 --> 35:08.805
AND YOU KILLED HIM SO YOU COULD
PRETEND IT NEVER HAPPENED.

35:08.807 --> 35:10.107
NOW ADMIT IT!

35:11.743 --> 35:13.743
I'D RATHER YOU SHOOT ME
THAN LIE

35:13.745 --> 35:15.879
AND SAY I KILLED MY SON.

35:17.516 --> 35:19.883
Cornell:
PUT THE GUN DOWN!

35:20.752 --> 35:22.486
I'M ON YOUR SIDE.

35:22.488 --> 35:26.123
PUT THE GUN DOWN NOW.

35:34.133 --> 35:36.166
[ GUN CLACKS ]

35:39.838 --> 35:41.138
HERE HE IS.

35:41.140 --> 35:43.640
[ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]

35:46.311 --> 35:47.477
THERE'S NO JUSTICE.

35:47.479 --> 35:50.213
YES, THERE IS,
MR. WILLIAMS.

35:50.215 --> 35:52.315
YOU JUST WON'T FIND IT
OUT HERE.

35:53.652 --> 35:55.552
LET'S GO.

35:55.554 --> 35:57.420
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

36:06.865 --> 36:08.932
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

36:12.604 --> 36:14.504
HOW DID YOU KNOW
I WAS MISSING?

36:14.506 --> 36:15.689
DAVE.

36:15.690 --> 36:16.873
WE TRACKED KEVIN'S
CELLPHONE SIGNAL

36:16.875 --> 36:18.775
AND NARROWED DOWN
THE LOCATION.

36:18.777 --> 36:21.178
YOU KNEW IT WAS KEVIN
THE WHOLE TIME.

36:21.180 --> 36:22.445
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

36:22.447 --> 36:23.847
WHAT ONE KNOWS
AND WHAT ONE CAN PROVE

36:23.849 --> 36:25.916
ARE TWO
VERY DIFFERENT THINGS.

36:27.419 --> 36:29.252
YOU COULD HAVE
PREVENTED THIS.

36:29.254 --> 36:30.420
HOW'S THAT?

36:30.422 --> 36:32.455
I OFFERED YOU PROTECTION.
YOU REFUSED IT.

36:32.457 --> 36:34.858
I TOLD YOU THE SERIOUSNESS
OF THIS SITUATION,

36:34.860 --> 36:36.393
AND YOU WENT
OFF THE RESERVATION.

36:36.395 --> 36:38.895
BUT YOU KNEW
WHO WAS AFTER ME.

36:38.897 --> 36:41.464
I CAN'T ARREST A CRIMINAL
BEFORE THEY ACT,

36:41.466 --> 36:43.833
BUT I DID GIVE HIM A WARNING,
WHICH YOU WITNESSED.

36:43.835 --> 36:45.635
AND SO NOW WHAT?

36:45.637 --> 36:48.872
KEVIN GETS OFF EASY
'CAUSE...I HAD IT COMING?

36:48.874 --> 36:51.775
I DID MY JOB.
THE MAN'S IN CUSTODY.

36:51.777 --> 36:53.810
NOW IT'S THE D.A.'s
PROBLEM,

36:53.812 --> 36:55.979
AND I CAN GO BACK
TO SOLVING TOM'S MURDER.

36:55.981 --> 36:58.415
THEY'RE GONNA BE TAKING YOU
TO THE HOSPITAL,

36:58.417 --> 37:02.552
AND A DETECTIVE WILL COME BY
AND GET YOUR FORMAL STATEMENT.

37:04.856 --> 37:06.923
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

37:14.967 --> 37:16.833
Dave: HEY.

37:16.835 --> 37:19.436
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
DADDY! [ CHUCKLES ]

37:19.438 --> 37:20.770
HEY, MONKEY.
Christy: HEY, HEY.

37:20.772 --> 37:22.706
LET'S GO SET
THE TABLE.

37:22.708 --> 37:24.441
HEY, MAN.
HI, DAD.

37:24.443 --> 37:25.709
HI.

37:25.711 --> 37:27.828
WE ORDERED PIZZA
FOR YOU.

37:27.829 --> 37:29.946
YEAH, I BROUGHT YOUR,
UH, STUFF BACK HERE.

37:29.948 --> 37:31.982
THANKS.

37:34.953 --> 37:36.586
ARE YOU OKAY?

37:36.588 --> 37:38.021
I MEAN, SHOULDN'T YOU STILL
BE IN THE HOSPITAL?

37:38.023 --> 37:39.823
DON'T THEY NEED
TO MAKE SURE?
I'M OKAY.

37:39.825 --> 37:40.924
I-I WOULDN'T BE HERE
IF I WASN'T.

37:40.926 --> 37:42.459
DO YOU WANT
TO SIT?

37:42.461 --> 37:43.893
YEAH.

37:47.466 --> 37:49.899
[ Sighing ]
OH, MAN.

37:52.404 --> 37:54.738
[ SIGHS ]

37:54.740 --> 37:56.740
PEPPERONI?

37:56.742 --> 37:57.841
YEAH. SURE, YEAH.
LOOKS GOOD.

37:57.843 --> 37:59.276
DAD,
YOU WANT THAT, TOO?

37:59.278 --> 38:01.444
DAD?

38:02.547 --> 38:04.547
WHAT?

38:07.986 --> 38:09.853
I'M NOT HUNGRY.

38:09.855 --> 38:11.621
SORRY.

38:16.695 --> 38:18.995
[ DOOR OPENS ]

38:18.997 --> 38:21.865
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

38:29.808 --> 38:31.675
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

38:31.677 --> 38:33.510
HEY.

38:35.681 --> 38:37.614
YOU OKAY, BUDDY?

38:37.616 --> 38:39.983
YEAH.

38:39.985 --> 38:42.852
BECAUSE IT WOULD BE TOTALLY FINE
IF YOU WEREN'T.

38:44.323 --> 38:46.456
SERIOUSLY.

38:49.761 --> 38:52.395
CAN'T TALK ABOUT IT.

38:52.397 --> 38:56.666
UM...

38:56.668 --> 38:59.002
I'M HERE FOR YOU
IF YOU NEED ME.

39:03.608 --> 39:05.742
I'M ASHAMED.

39:08.046 --> 39:10.914
YOU'RE ASHAMED?

39:10.916 --> 39:14.951
WHAT -- Y-YOU HAVE NOTHING
TO BE ASHAMED ABOUT.

39:14.953 --> 39:16.519
YES, I DO.

39:19.091 --> 39:21.358
TOM WAS KILLED.

39:23.095 --> 39:25.595
AND I TURNED MYSELF
INTO THE VICTIM.

39:46.651 --> 39:49.386
[ CLICKING ]

39:56.628 --> 39:57.927
[ KEYBOARD CLACKS ]

40:02.567 --> 40:05.001
ARE YOU COMING TO BED?

40:07.873 --> 40:10.440
YEAH.
I'LL BE THERE IN A MINUTE.

40:27.125 --> 40:29.192
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

40:33.899 --> 40:35.899
[ GRUNTS ]
BEN! BEN!

40:35.901 --> 40:37.600
WAIT! STOP!
I DIDN'T PRINT IT!

40:37.602 --> 40:38.868
I HAD TO GET
YOUR ATTENTION!

40:38.870 --> 40:40.937
I'M NOT -- OHH!

40:43.642 --> 40:44.974
[ SNIFFS ]

40:46.945 --> 40:51.614
I'M --
I AM AFTER CORNELL.

40:51.616 --> 40:53.583
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

40:53.585 --> 40:55.718
AND I NEED YOUR HELP.
